{"title":"社员的心","authors":["李镇欧"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李镇欧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个桃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子进果园忘了弯腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不小心碰掉了一个桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃儿滚在草地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真把他的心儿痛坏了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急忙拾起瞧一瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红朴朴的果实还满好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘下羊肚毛巾包起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急忙去把队长找。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小两口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红霞天，红霞地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小两口假日走亲戚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿柳林，过麦地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛抬头见河水冲垮了堤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男的跳下挡缺口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女的边喊边堵泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十张铁锨齐赶来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场危险才免去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女的涂成“花花脸”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男的穿上“花花衣”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二人对瞧呵呵笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比见了亲戚还欢喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找阿爷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一天太阳已落山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不见阿爷回家转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里村外找了个遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才发现他蹲在小路中间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昏花的老眼盯着地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像在月光下面寻针尖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运麦车上掉下了穗头儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一个个往篮里捡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说：“饭都快凉啦！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿爷说：“不拾干净吃不下饭。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说：“阿奶和爹妈都在把你等。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿爷说：“我还得去给粗心的年轻人提个意见！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}